**Auto-connect logic:** `resolveConnectedVariant` maps neighbor booleans `{north, south, east, west}` to the correct piece per type — isolated→pole/column, end cap→small piece, straight→wall, corner (2 perpendicular)→corner piece. `resolveConnectedRotation` returns `π/2` for E-W aligned segments. When `connections` is passed to `FenceModel`, it uses both functions; without it, explicit `variant`+`rotationY` are used directly.

